VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT DB::raw\(|selectRaw\(|whereRaw\(|->query\(\s*\$|mysqli_query\(|PDO::query\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:$wpdb->prepare|esc_sql|bindParam && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects raw/dynamic SQL construction in framework and DB access calls.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Wordpress Raw SQL Query Construction.
